{"tid":183712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"5男輪姦少女仲fb直播 40人收睇冇人報警","createTime":"2017-04-02T10:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T07:25:37.000Z","uid":69289,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bdf4c8a515e47557874cde304b0f883268c0c348","tid":183712,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170402/large/1491110715_207b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170402%2Flarge%2F1491110715_207b.jpg&h=b5b9e8fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國芝加哥一名15歲少女遭「5或6名男性」輪姦，過程更透過社交網Facebook直播，警方周六宣佈拘捕一名涉案的14歲少年，相信將會有更多涉案人士落網。<br />\n<br />\n芝加哥警方在周六晚的記者會上表示，疑犯涉嚴重性侵犯、製作兒童色情物品及發佈兒童色情物品等嚴重罪行被捕，料於當地時間周日早上發佈更多消息。<br />\n事發於上月19日，5至6名男子性侵受害人更在fb直播，受害人母親艾爾金斯（Stacey Elkins）發現片段後，前往警署直接接觸警司約翰遜（Eddie Johnson），讓他得悉事件尋求協助。<br />\n約翰遜看畢片段後表示「慘不忍睹」，除因內容變態，更因當時有約40人觀看直播卻無一人報警，警方事後找到受害人位置並將她送醫。<br />\n美聯社"},{"pid":"62394f37479a5ab873a17495497a3b07ab03c267","tid":183712,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:09:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170402/56512402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170402%2F56512402&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UePiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=05936bdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170402%2F56512402&h=ed5b39e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170402/56512402</a>"},{"pid":"6550717a6a69484f4d497af622cd9810592283e2","tid":183712,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d92ccef3b727de3e244d257f3d3c59e38c85afa","tid":183712,"uid":1315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":